内存管理问题（GC 问题）可能也是独立的性能诱因。\n\n### 裁决结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context deadline exceeded\", \"AdService--gc\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"Memory pressure on aiops-k8s-03 correlates with the performance issues of adservice. The presence of 'context deadline exceeded' errors and 'AdService--gc' logs suggests intertwined factors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"'node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes' metrics show significant memory drop on aiops-k8s-03. Simultaneous logs highlight GC activities and deadline errors in adservice.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"AdService shows significant garbage collection (GC) logs linked with context deadline exceeded errors, indicating potential internal inefficiencies in memory management.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs reference 'context deadline exceeded' and associated 'AdService--gc' events multiple times.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n明确认定：假设得到支持，`aiops-k8s-03` 的内存压力可能是 `adservice` 延迟问题的重要因素，但同时需要更多调研 `adservice` 垃圾回收的有效性及其内部资源管理是否出现性能瓶颈。这将决定后续的优化方向是基础设施配置优化还是应用层优化。"}
